<br>
any Thoughts?! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> TirBM</span><br> <span class=usertitle>Unregistered User</span><br>   <font color=#000000>(1/7/03 6:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> WTF?</span><hr size=1> WTF? Peircing? As a blademaster? come on man IMO thats dumb <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=craess>craess</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://media.ign.com/boards/images/icons/matrix_pills.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#000000>(1/7/03 6:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=74.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: WTF?</span><hr size=1> 50 parry/ 44 peirce/ rest in cdw is a decent template...<br>
<br>
